snippet.title: Lava Fever - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
A volcano dropping, fireball dodging, soul sacrificing ride that puts your reflexes to the test.
More info on http://lavafever.com. Get the game on the App Store here: http://apple.co/1J3FC9H

Lava Fever is a 2d action arcade game for your iPhone.

follow us on http://facebook.com/happyvolcanogames and http://twitter.com/hvgames
